ESRB’s Trichet Says There’s a Global Crisis of Sovereign Risk

-- B y   J a n a   R a n d o w
-- 
2011-10-11T08:24:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-11/esrb-s-trichet-says-there-s-a-global-crisis-of-sovereign-risk.html
European Central Bank President
 Jean-Claude Trichet  said that the world faces a crisis of
sovereign risk.  “We have to take collectively, as a college, decisions in
order to cope with a systemic crisis that has a global nature
and that we are the epicenter of,” Trichet told lawmakers in
Brussels today in his capacity as head of the European Systemic
Risk Board. “We are the epicenter but it’s a challenge for all
sovereign signatures.’’  “The main issue for us is to restore the credibility of
the sovereign,” he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jana Randow in Frankfurt at 
 jrandow@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Craig Stirling at 
 cstirling1@bloomberg.net  